    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with everything so it runs smoothly and looks great too! It\u2019s the perfect ride if you\u2019re looking for something dependable and well-cared for without the brand-new price tag. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make someone very happy. Drop me a message if you want to come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a corrected Double-VANOS system for peak volumetric efficiency. This example is mechanically sorted, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already completed and rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, channeling power through the factory variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and an upgraded cooling system to handle spirited sessions. While the exterior shows minor signs of use, the internal components and drivetrain integrity make this a turn-key performance machine for the purist.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Regular maintenance records available. Clean interior. Mechanically sound. No major accidents.",
      "price": 32000.0,
