    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been so good to me and is still running like a champ! It\u2019s been well-loved and properly maintained, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend road trips. It\u2019s in great shape and just waiting for a new home. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
