    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering with this S54-powered E46 M3. Featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 7,900 RPM redline, this example delivers exceptional throttle response through its 6-speed manual transmission. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system is in excellent working order. Equipped with a limited-slip variable M differential and refreshed suspension geometry, it offers precise turn-in and mechanical grip. A well-maintained driver\u2019s car for the purist seeking analog feedback and linear power delivery.",
